CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 30, 1946, pg. 27, reads: "Planning 'YW' Confab - Members of the Religious Projects Committee of the Centre Avenue YWCA completed plans last Friday for the fourth annual Religious Leaders' Workshop to be held at the 'YW' March 28-29. Included on [in] the photo are Mmes. Elsie Meeks, Zella Hardy, Leafie V. White, Mary Johnston, LaVerne Davis, Lena Hughes, Octavia Dandridge, Mary White, Grace McCray, Alma A. Polk, Ethel Gohanna, Golden Young May, Misses Dorothy Guinn, Mollie Faison, Elmira Higgins and the Rev. H. N. Robinson. - Harris Photo."
